          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>The Metropolitan Planning Enhancement Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires that transportation projects included in an adopted metropolitan area transportation plan be selected through a publicly available transparent process using criteria that directly support specified factors, national transportation goals, and applicable state transportation goals.</p>]]></text>
